		<RichText x="738" y="479" width="427" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">尼尼安涅用力敲击地面，产生喷溅造成<span color="#7fbfff">100%</span><span>伤害，并在正前方产生3道扩散型水喷，水喷造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">100%,25%,10%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="703" width="437" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">尼尼安涅疯狂进行旋转，接触造成<span color="#7fbfff">40%</span><span>伤害，命中玩家或技能超时后，将进行一段上挑，造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">100%</span><span>伤害，同时生成一个水喷，造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
